title: Supercars.Exposed-Speed2008-AstonDB9-WRXsti-ontrack
description: SuperCars Exposed, Speed Channel (US) 2008, Hosted by Tanner Foust, 22 mins.  Cars featured: 2008 Aston Martin DB9, Race-prepped Subaru WRX STi with 500hp, 2008 Dodge Viper SRT10 with 600hp.  Includes street and race track evaluation of Aston Martin, including race against the Subaru, prepped by Harmon Motive and driven by J.C. Meynet.  MP4 file, H264 codec, 640x480, captured from digital SDTV.  More episodes to come from tallearthling.
